透囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你睇睇下面個List<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E8%BB%8D%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25BB%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E9%2596%2593%25E8%25AB%259C%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%25A1%25A8&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdIleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=192a6fa6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E8%BB%8D%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8</a><br />\n<br />\n呢度只係中共滲透國民黨嘅千分之一<br />\n<br />\n下至秘書仔<br />\n上至國民黨參謀、司令官、少將、中將<br />\n<br />\n成班都係卧底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打毛賊都打得hea啲<br />\n<br />\n不過呢個case喺香港用唔到<br />\n<br />\n由孫中山搞「聯俄容共」開始<br />\n有部分國民黨將領都同情、認同共產黨<br />\n所以先會甘於做共狗卧底<br />\n<br />\n(呢部分可能有錯，唔太熟中史，有錯請糾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n警犬由主權移交到而家都冇當過自己係公僕，成個內部嘅Mindset同目標都冇放過市民入眼內，所以入到去洗完腦仲可以做到手足嘅機會幾乎係零"},{"pid":"ac7213b14d2ae2a5ad24a33770e5a55ef763a00d","tid":1938821,"uid":228945,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ffb277e8c671b31596acff6f2946b6f329800761","tid":1938821,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"83e3b3d2f229e471457e5f30fca61a3b230799d6","tid":1938821,"uid":228945,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"78ec2fdb35c62acd3